---
layout: base.njk
title: 專欄文章｜溪水邊 Stream Side
description: 溪水邊 Stream Side 專欄文章 — 關於心理、繪本與租書店觀察的深度閱讀。
activeNav: articles
jsonLd: |
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "Blog",
    "name": "溪水邊專欄",
    "description": "關於心理諮商、兒童閱讀與書店觀察的深度文章",
    "url": "https://streamside.tw/articles/",
    "author": {
      "@type": "Person",
      "name": "溪水邊創辦人"
    }
  }
pageStyle: |
  .sidebar-sticky { position: sticky; top: 88px; }
pageScript: |
  <script>
    // Tag filter
    function filterTags(btn, tag) {
      document.querySelectorAll('.tag-btn').forEach(b => b.classList.remove('active'));
      btn.classList.add('active');
      const articles = document.querySelectorAll('.article-card');
      articles.forEach(a => {
        if (tag === 'all') {
          a.style.display = '';
        } else {
          const tags = a.dataset.tags || '';
          a.style.display = tags.includes(tag) ? '' : 'none';
        }
      });
    }

    // Show sidebar on desktop
    function updateSidebar() {
      const sidebar = document.querySelector('aside');
      if (window.innerWidth >= 1024) {
        sidebar.style.display = 'block';
      } else {
        sidebar.style.display = 'none';
      }
    }
    updateSidebar();
    window.addEventListener('resize', updateSidebar);
  </script>
---

<!-- ══════════════ PAGE HERO ══════════════ -->
<div class="page-hero">
  <p style="font-size:0.8rem;letter-spacing:0.18em;color:var(--straw);margin-bottom:0.5rem;text-transform:uppercase;">Articles</p>
  <h1>專欄文章</h1>
  <p>每一篇文字，都是一次溫柔的相遇。</p>
</div>

<!-- ══════════════ TAG FILTER ══════════════ -->
<div style="max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 1.5rem 2.5rem;" role="search" aria-label="文章標籤過濾">
  <p style="font-size:0.8rem;color:rgba(67,52,48,0.5);margin-bottom:1rem;letter-spacing:0.05em;">依主題瀏覽：</p>
  <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:0.6rem;" id="tag-filter">
    <button class="tag-btn active" data-tag="all" onclick="filterTags(this,'all')">全部</button>
    <button class="tag-btn" data-tag="心理" onclick="filterTags(this,'心理')">#心理</button>
    <button class="tag-btn" data-tag="繪本" onclick="filterTags(this,'繪本')">#繪本</button>
    <button class="tag-btn" data-tag="租書店觀察" onclick="filterTags(this,'租書店觀察')">#租書店觀察</button>
    <button class="tag-btn" data-tag="親子" onclick="filterTags(this,'親子')">#親子</button>
    <button class="tag-btn" data-tag="自我探索" onclick="filterTags(this,'自我探索')">#自我探索</button>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ══════════════ SIDEBAR LAYOUT ══════════════ -->
<div class="sidebar-layout" style="padding-bottom:5rem;">

  <!-- ── ARTICLE LIST ── -->
  <section aria-labelledby="article-list-heading">
    <h2 id="article-list-heading" style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(67,52,48,0.4);letter-spacing:0.08em;margin-bottom:1.5rem;font-weight:400;">顯示所有文章</h2>

    {% if articles.length %}
      {% for article in articles %}
        <article class="article-card" data-tags="{{ article.tags | join(' ') }}">
          <a href="{{ ('/articles/' + article.slug + '/') | url }}" class="article-thumb" style="display:block;text-decoration:none;">
            {% if article.image %}
              <img src="{{ article.image | url }}" alt="{{ article.title }}" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;">
            {% else %}
              <span>封面圖<br>Placeholder</span>
            {% endif %}
          </a>
          <div class="article-body">
            <p class="date">{{ article.date | dateDisplay }}</p>
            <div style="display:flex;gap:0.4rem;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">
              {% for tag in article.tags %}
                <span class="tag">#{{ tag }}</span>
              {% endfor %}
            </div>
            <h3><a href="{{ ('/articles/' + article.slug + '/') | url }}" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:none;transition:color 0.2s;" onmouseover="this.style.color='var(--straw)'" onmouseout="this.style.color='inherit'">{{ article.title }}</a></h3>
            <p class="summary-label">3 秒摘要</p>
            <p class="summary">{{ article.summary }}</p>
            <a href="{{ ('/articles/' + article.slug + '/') | url }}" style="display:inline-block;margin-top:0.75rem;font-size:0.82rem;color:var(--straw);font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.04em;transition:opacity 0.2s;" onmouseover="this.style.opacity='0.7'" onmouseout="this.style.opacity='1'">閱讀全文 →</a>
          </div>
        </article>
      {% endfor %}
    {% else %}
      <!-- Placeholder articles shown when Notion is not connected -->
      <article class="article-card" data-tags="心理 自我探索">
        <div class="article-thumb">
          <span>封面圖<br>Placeholder</span>
        </div>
        <div class="article-body">
          <p class="date">2026年3月28日</p>
          <div style="display:flex;gap:0.4rem;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">
            <span class="tag">#心理</span>
            <span class="tag">#自我探索</span>
          </div>
          <h3><span class="placeholder-text">文章標題一 Article Title 1 Placeholder — 關於自我探索的深度文章</span></h3>
          <p class="summary-label">3 秒摘要</p>
          <p class="summary"><span class="placeholder-text">文章重點摘要佔位符：讀者能在3秒內理解本文核心價值。3-second summary for AEO: the key takeaway a reader needs before deciding to read on. Article Excerpt Placeholder.</span></p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="article-card" data-tags="繪本 親子">
        <div class="article-thumb">
          <span>封面圖<br>Placeholder</span>
        </div>
        <div class="article-body">
          <p class="date">2026年3月15日</p>
          <div style="display:flex;gap:0.4rem;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">
            <span class="tag">#繪本</span>
            <span class="tag">#親子</span>
          </div>
          <h3><span class="placeholder-text">文章標題二 Article Title 2 Placeholder — 關於繪本與親子陪伴的溫暖分享</span></h3>
          <p class="summary-label">3 秒摘要</p>
          <p class="summary"><span class="placeholder-text">文章重點摘要佔位符：這篇文章分享了哪一本繪本以及它如何在親子關係中發揮作用。3-second summary Placeholder.</span></p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="article-card" data-tags="租書店觀察">
        <div class="article-thumb">
          <span>封面圖<br>Placeholder</span>
        </div>
        <div class="article-body">
          <p class="date">2026年2月28日</p>
          <div style="display:flex;gap:0.4rem;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">
            <span class="tag">#租書店觀察</span>
          </div>
          <h3><span class="placeholder-text">文章標題三 Article Title 3 Placeholder — 在租書店裡看見的人情溫度</span></h3>
          <p class="summary-label">3 秒摘要</p>
          <p class="summary"><span class="placeholder-text">文章重點摘要佔位符：在書店的日常中，那些讓人動容的人與書的相遇瞬間。3-second summary Placeholder.</span></p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="article-card" data-tags="心理 自我探索">
        <div class="article-thumb">
          <span>封面圖<br>Placeholder</span>
        </div>
        <div class="article-body">
          <p class="date">2026年2月14日</p>
          <div style="display:flex;gap:0.4rem;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">
            <span class="tag">#心理</span>
            <span class="tag">#自我探索</span>
          </div>
          <h3><span class="placeholder-text">文章標題四 Article Title 4 Placeholder — 心理諮商的日常觀察與思考</span></h3>
          <p class="summary-label">3 秒摘要</p>
          <p class="summary"><span class="placeholder-text">文章重點摘要佔位符：從諮商現場出發，談一個關於接納與改變的核心概念。3-second summary Placeholder.</span></p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="article-card" data-tags="繪本 租書店觀察">
        <div class="article-thumb">
          <span>封面圖<br>Placeholder</span>
        </div>
        <div class="article-body">
          <p class="date">2026年1月30日</p>
          <div style="display:flex;gap:0.4rem;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">
            <span class="tag">#繪本</span>
            <span class="tag">#租書店觀察</span>
          </div>
          <h3><span class="placeholder-text">文章標題五 Article Title 5 Placeholder — 那些陪孩子選書的午後時光</span></h3>
          <p class="summary-label">3 秒摘要</p>
          <p class="summary"><span class="placeholder-text">文章重點摘要佔位符：選書不只是選故事，也是選一種看世界的方式。3-second summary Placeholder.</span></p>
        </div>
      </article>
    {% endif %}

    <!-- Load more placeholder -->
    <div style="text-align:center;margin-top:2rem;">
      <button class="btn-outline">載入更多文章</button>
    </div>

  </section>

  <!-- ── SIDEBAR ── -->
  <aside aria-label="側邊欄" style="display:none;" class="lg-show">
    <div class="sidebar-sticky">

      <!-- Recommended — 自動取最新 3 篇 -->
      <div style="background:white;border-radius:1rem;padding:1.5rem;margin-bottom:1.5rem;box-shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(140,106,93,0.06);">
        <h3 style="font-size:0.9rem;color:var(--oak);font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.08em;margin-bottom:1.25rem;">推薦閱讀</h3>
        <ul style="list-style:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1rem;">
          {% if articles.length %}
            {% for rec in articles | slice(0, 3) %}
              <li {% if not loop.first %}style="border-top:1px solid rgba(140,106,93,0.1);padding-top:1rem;"{% endif %}>
                <a href="{{ ('/articles/' + rec.slug + '/') | url }}" style="display:block;text-decoration:none;">
                  <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:var(--oak);font-weight:600;line-height:1.5;">{{ rec.title }}</p>
                  <p style="font-size:0.75rem;color:rgba(67,52,48,0.45);margin-top:0.2rem;">{{ rec.date | dateDisplay }}</p>
                </a>
              </li>
            {% endfor %}
          {% else %}
            <li><p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:rgba(67,52,48,0.4);">文章更新後顯示</p></li>
          {% endif %}
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Hot Tags -->
      <div style="background:white;border-radius:1rem;padding:1.5rem;margin-bottom:1.5rem;box-shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(140,106,93,0.06);">
        <h3 style="font-size:0.9rem;color:var(--oak);font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.08em;margin-bottom:1.25rem;">熱門標籤</h3>
        <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:0.5rem;">
          <span class="tag">#心理</span>
          <span class="tag">#繪本</span>
          <span class="tag">#租書店觀察</span>
          <span class="tag">#親子</span>
          <span class="tag">#自我探索</span>
          <span class="tag">#諮商</span>
          <span class="tag">#書單</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--oak),#6b4f45);border-radius:1rem;padding:1.5rem;text-align:center;">
        <p style="color:var(--rice);font-size:0.88rem;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:1rem;">想要在溪水邊找到專屬的陪伴？</p>
        <a href="{{ '/events/' | url }}" class="btn-primary" style="font-size:0.82rem;padding:0.6rem 1.5rem;">預約諮商</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </aside>
</div>
